Abaminisitiri b’ububanyi n’amahanga b’Ubwongereza, Ubufaransa mu kongera ingufu mu bikorwa by’amahoro bya DRC - 2002-01-18
Ku wa mbere, abaminisitiri b’ububanyi n’amahanga b’Ubwongereza n’Ubufaransa berekeje muri Repubulika Iharanira Demokarasi ya Kongo kugira ngo batangire urugendo rw’iminsi itatu, bazenguruka ibihugu bine by'akarere gafite ibibazo muri Afurika yo hagati.
Ubu butumwa buzayoborwa n’umunyamabanga w’ububanyi n’amahanga w’Ubwongereza Jack Straw na mugenzi we w’Ubufaransa Hubert Vedrine.
Bazasura Repubulika Iharanira Demokarasi ya Kongo, u Rwanda, Uburundi na Uganda.
Intego yabo y'ibanze ni uguhumeka umwuka w'ubuzima bushya mu nzira y'amahoro muri Kongo yibasiwe n'intambara.
By'umwihariko, Abongereza n'Abafaransa bifuza kubona ikurwaho ry'ingabo z'amahanga zishyigikiye guverinoma ya Kongo-Kinshasa, gusezerera mu gisirikare inyeshyamba zigarurira igice cya kabiri cy'igihugu, n'ibiganiro by'amahoro kugira ngo amakimbirane arangire.
Umunyamabanga w’ububanyi n’amahanga w’Ubwongereza Straw yavuze ko ubwo butumwa bufite intego nini yo kureba niba Kongo itazaba indi Afuganisitani.
Ati: "Ku ya 11 Nzeri birihutirwa cyane ko dufata ingamba zo kurwanya ibihugu byananiranye, kandi bikinanirana".
