Aho niharangira hazakurikiraho Kigali kugira ngo baganire na Perezida w’u Rwanda, Paul Kagame, n’umuyobozi w’inyeshyamba zo muri Repubulika Iharanira Demokarasi ya Kongo, Adolphe Onusumba.
