Yavuze ko yizera ko ibyaha by'ihohotera rishingiye ku gitsina bizagabanuka cyane imirwano iramutse ihagaze.
Umurwanashyaka Donatella Rostagno, ukomoka mu ihuriro ry’iburayi rikorera muri Afurika yo hagati, yaherekeje Bihamba mu rugendo rwe muri Amerika.
Yavuze ko ashyigikiye imirimo ikorwa n’uhagarariye Umuryango w’abibumbye ushinzwe ihohoterwa rishingiye ku gitsina mu makimbirane.
Rostagno yavuze kandi ko abyumva, ariko ko, umuryango mpuzamahanga udakora ibishoboka byose ngo uhagarike intambara ya Congo, nubwo hariyo akazi katoroshye ku Muryango w'Abibumbye ko kubungabunga amahoro.
Rostagno ati: "Ibyinshi mu bikorwa bikorwa kugira ngo harebwe ingaruka, gukorana n'abagore bahohotewe, ariko ntibihagije kugira ngo harebwe ibitera gufata ku ngufu n'amakimbirane."
